  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Reaktor</strong> is a modern spin on the classic block-stacking game! Features 360° block stacking, mind bending goodness. For one to four players: team up with friends in local co-op, and climb the leaderboards to fame.     </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>The Features: </strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Combines classic tetromino gameplay with chains and combos.</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >X-ray, zipper, and zig-zag techniques not found in any other tetromino game.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Play with up to four friends in local co-op. </p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>The Fans:</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>\"Beautiful minimalist 4-player radial tetris, with x-ray powerup for added depth.\"</i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>\"For the fans of Tetris, this one is a real breath of fresh air\". </i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>\"Chain reactions can be strategically produced as in the game PuyoPuyo Tetris\"</i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>\"Like someone put Tetrominos and Super Hexagon in a blender\"</i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>The Screens:</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2950640/extras/ac7207c04829d13ec69606a345ebb396.poster.avif?t=1745154219\" width=512 height=512 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2950640/extras/ac7207c04829d13ec69606a345ebb396.webm?t=1745154219\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2950640/extras/ac7207c04829d13ec69606a345ebb396.mp4?t=1745154219\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Create Chain Reactions!</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2950640/extras/ad1b5dce08ed0287b45ae3a5efe7d0f2.poster.avif?t=1745154219\" width=620 height=480 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2950640/extras/ad1b5dce08ed0287b45ae3a5efe7d0f2.webm?t=1745154219\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2950640/extras/ad1b5dce08ed0287b45ae3a5efe7d0f2.mp4?t=1745154219\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Team up with with friends to build faster and make larger chains.</strong> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2950640/extras/69e101427972c5a93186eb9ab4d5072c.poster.avif?t=1745154219\" width=620 height=480 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2950640/extras/69e101427972c5a93186eb9ab4d5072c.webm?t=1745154219\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2950640/extras/69e101427972c5a93186eb9ab4d5072c.mp4?t=1745154219\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Make huge chains with advanced techniques</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2950640/extras/f635afe5dc6e9671a17387c90a13d7a5.poster.avif?t=1745154219\" width=640 height=400 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2950640/extras/f635afe5dc6e9671a17387c90a13d7a5.webm?t=1745154219\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2950640/extras/f635afe5dc6e9671a17387c90a13d7a5.mp4?t=1745154219\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Two players, one keyboard!</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2950640/extras/ae1c1e547bbfec67382aecc673a5715b.poster.avif?t=1745154219\" width=620 height=480 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2950640/extras/ae1c1e547bbfec67382aecc673a5715b.webm?t=1745154219\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2950640/extras/ae1c1e547bbfec67382aecc673a5715b.mp4?t=1745154219\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>The Reaktor Story:</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>One day, a bored engineer at the Chernobyl nuclear power plant modified the SKALA control program with a score function so it would be more fun to play. He began making larger and larger reactions, until one day he messed up and caused a meltdown.</i> <i><strong>But he was addicted.</strong></i> <i>Years later, he sneaked back into the rubble, stole the modified control code and published it as an internationally acclaimed video game called REAKTOR.</i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2950640/extras/d68ecc1960b0e05a25623c082179aaa8.avif?t=1745154219\" width=700 height=464 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Reaktor</strong> is a modern spin on the classic block-stacking game! Features 360° block stacking, mind bending goodness. For one to four players: team up with friends in local co-op, and climb the leaderboards to fame.     </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>The Features: </strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Combines classic tetromino gameplay with chains and combos.</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >X-ray, zipper, and zig-zag techniques not found in any other tetromino game.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Play with up to four friends in local co-op. </p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>The Fans:</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>\"Beautiful minimalist 4-player radial tetris, with x-ray powerup for added depth.\"</i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>\"For the fans of Tetris, this one is a real breath of fresh air\". </i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>\"Chain reactions can be strategically produced as in the game PuyoPuyo Tetris\"</i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>\"Like someone put Tetrominos and Super Hexagon in a blender\"</i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>The Screens:</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2950640/extras/ac7207c04829d13ec69606a345ebb396.poster.avif?t=1745154219\" width=512 height=512 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2950640/extras/ac7207c04829d13ec69606a345ebb396.webm?t=1745154219\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2950640/extras/ac7207c04829d13ec69606a345ebb396.mp4?t=1745154219\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Create Chain Reactions!</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2950640/extras/ad1b5dce08ed0287b45ae3a5efe7d0f2.poster.avif?t=1745154219\" width=620 height=480 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2950640/extras/ad1b5dce08ed0287b45ae3a5efe7d0f2.webm?t=1745154219\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2950640/extras/ad1b5dce08ed0287b45ae3a5efe7d0f2.mp4?t=1745154219\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Team up with with friends to build faster and make larger chains.</strong> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2950640/extras/69e101427972c5a93186eb9ab4d5072c.poster.avif?t=1745154219\" width=620 height=480 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2950640/extras/69e101427972c5a93186eb9ab4d5072c.webm?t=1745154219\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2950640/extras/69e101427972c5a93186eb9ab4d5072c.mp4?t=1745154219\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Make huge chains with advanced techniques</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2950640/extras/f635afe5dc6e9671a17387c90a13d7a5.poster.avif?t=1745154219\" width=640 height=400 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2950640/extras/f635afe5dc6e9671a17387c90a13d7a5.webm?t=1745154219\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2950640/extras/f635afe5dc6e9671a17387c90a13d7a5.mp4?t=1745154219\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Two players, one keyboard!</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2950640/extras/ae1c1e547bbfec67382aecc673a5715b.poster.avif?t=1745154219\" width=620 height=480 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2950640/extras/ae1c1e547bbfec67382aecc673a5715b.webm?t=1745154219\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2950640/extras/ae1c1e547bbfec67382aecc673a5715b.mp4?t=1745154219\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>The Reaktor Story:</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>One day, a bored engineer at the Chernobyl nuclear power plant modified the SKALA control program with a score function so it would be more fun to play. He began making larger and larger reactions, until one day he messed up and caused a meltdown.</i> <i><strong>But he was addicted.</strong></i> <i>Years later, he sneaked back into the rubble, stole the modified control code and published it as an internationally acclaimed video game called REAKTOR.</i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2950640/extras/d68ecc1960b0e05a25623c082179aaa8.avif?t=1745154219\" width=700 height=464 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
